title.rendered: AFN WHEEL CARRIER & JERRY HOLDER TO SUIT ISUZU D-MAX (2012 – 2016)

content.rendered:
AFN Wheel Carrier & Jerry Holder to suit Isuzu D-MAX (2012-2016) is available now at Automax 4×4!

The AFN wheel carrier & jerry holder to suit the Isuzu D-MAX includes;

  • Single Wheel Carrier
  • Single Jerry Can Holder
  • Built-in Towbar
  • Rated Recovery Points
  • Hi-Lift Jack Points
  • Matte Black Powder Coated

Click here to check out our great range of products suited to your Isuzu D-MAX!

For more 4×4 inspiration follow us on Instagram and Facebook
